### Hadith 2:694

*Narrated Urwa from Aisha:*

Some people performed Tawaf (of the Kaba) after the morning prayer and
then sat to listen to a preacher till sunrise, and then they stood up
for the prayer. Then Aisha commented, "Those people kept on sitting till
it was the time in which the prayer is disliked and after that they
stood up for the prayer."

